lu_part1: Dee vill huet ass vill gehäit,
en_literal_translation_p1: He who has much is much envied,
en_literal_translation_p2: he who has nothing even more.
en_closest_real_corresponding_saying_p1: The more you have, the more you are envied,
en_closest_real_corresponding_saying_p2: but the poor are pitied even more.
